text.section:
The report shall include:
A description of activities undertaken in accordance with this subtitle;
The costs of the activities undertaken in accordance with this subtitle;
The findings of the research and monitoring program, including the current levels and anticipated significant adverse effects and future trends of acid deposition in the State;
Recommended State responses, when appropriate, to federal legislative or regulatory initiatives; and
Potential options to evaluate acid deposition and its potential adverse effects in the State.
